{"tid":2060060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王毅：「中国從不主動欺壓別人」","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T17:00:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6799b96e3468a47cb70d4628c4c90e41290055","tid":2060060,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:05:20.000Z","msg":"中國外交部長日前回應媒體提問，表示中國奉行的始終是「獨立自主的和平外交」政策，並聲明「中國從來不會主動欺凌他人，對於蓄意的中傷，我們一定會作出有力回擊，堅決捍衛國家的榮譽和民族尊嚴」。<br />\n<br />\n對於王毅表示「中國從來不會主動欺凌他人」，日本網友們在5ch展開了相當熱烈的討論，紛紛嘲諷「Nice Joke」、「說謊就跟呼吸一樣自然呢」、「想知道西藏、新疆、香港跟台灣的意見」、「全部反著看，就能很好理解了」、「真想在中共幹部們身上裝測謊器」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/11/2603919-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F11%2F2603919-XXL.jpg&h=50ec6f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王毅的一席話對於日本網友來說可說是「很難笑的笑話」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=760130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D760130&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=1363d8b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D760130&h=b5c753a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=760130</a>"},{"pid":"571e6bd25221db82a9ce4db3340bcb2f949add19","tid":2060060,"uid":73192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"係會用坦克碌鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e93e30dc389979d8bf68df212580131a851bdb","tid":2060060,"uid":115096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"中國嘅恐龍係唔咬人"},{"pid":"84431528026477470ce92d2a3e785b1daf41a5fc","tid":2060060,"uid":99172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"我想講佢塊臉勁膠 係咪打咗野 勁僵硬"},{"pid":"3c82ee8c31cfecc6d65b98eb9d51f19d728cae63","tid":2060060,"uid":32391,"like":4